===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|t|pin=shàng yǒu tiāntáng, xià yǒu sūháng|pint=shang4you3tian1tang2xia4you3su1hang2|tra=上有天堂，下有蘇杭|sim=上有天堂，下有苏杭|rs=一02}}
